LOad balancer :- 
if multiple users go through a single VM then its server may slow so in that situation load balancer distributes
incoming traffics across multiple servers / VMs .
benefits :- better performance 
            high availability
            no single server overload 
    
    CONTENT DELIVERY NETWORK (CDN):-
    if different country's network /server wants to connect with another country's server  the it have to connect
    with nearest CDN server for faster delivery of data . 
    {cdn stores copies of content closer  to users for faster delivery .}
    benefits :- faster loading 
                better user experience 
                reduced load on main server .
                 